Description: A beautiful music player for Linux
 Melodia is an elegant GTK4 music player built with libadwaita.
 It features a dark luxury aesthetic, animated equaliser bars,
 album art display, and supports MP3, FLAC, OGG, M4A and more.
 .
 Powered by GStreamer for gapless-ready playback.
